&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
  &lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;td class=&quot;diff-marker&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;td class=&quot;diff-addedline&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;Also present at the inaugural meeting was [[Stella Thomas]], who would go on to become the first woman magistrate in West Africa.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
